-- India's JSW Steel in Talks to Invest in JFE Holding's Unit, Nikkei Reports
-- B y   T a k   K u m a k u r a
-- 2010-10-03T21:41:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-03/india-s-jsw-steel-in-talks-to-invest-in-jfe-holding-s-unit-nikkei-says.html
JSW Steel Ltd., India’s third-biggest
steelmaker, is in talks to invest in JFE Holdings Inc.’s JFE
Steel unit, the Nikkei newspaper reported, citing an interview
with JSW Vice Chairman Sajjan Jindal.   JSW may acquire less than 5 percent of JFE Steel within the
next two years, the newspaper said. JFE Steel this year bought
about 15 percent of JSW, the report said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Takehiko Kumakura at 
 tkumakura@bloomberg.net  